💰 Coin: PEPE
💵 Price: $0.00001234
📈 24h Change: +45.7%
📊 Volume: $2,500,000
🎯 Confidence: 92.1%

⚡ RUNNER IDENTIFIED
⏰ 12:15:32

Signal by: TrenchCoat Pro AI

[📊 View Chart] [💰 Trade]
[🤖 TrenchCoat Pro]
```

